Text: I found a minor broadcast glitch on the video at around 12:30. It lasts about a second and doesn't render the video unwatchable, but I'm just letting everyone know in advance.
I downloaded and it lost its file extension and whenever I try to load the file list it doesnt show the file so can someone tell me what type of file this is?

@mhamer6

That's odd, but it's a matroska file, so you want to add ".mkv" at the end of the filename. (excluding the quotation marks of course)

Alright thanks. VLC could play it for me without the file extension but it bothered me because I'm OCD. BTW thanks for uploading the only full version on here, the one thats getting all the credit is only the first 11 minutes
